article_title: Killed Hamas leader Sinwar 'spent years planning 7 October attack' - Israeli military spokesman.
sentence: At  a  news  briefing  late  on  Saturday,  Israeli  military  spokesman  Daniel  Hagari  gave  more  details  on  the  death  of  former  Hamas  leader,  Yahya  Sinwar,  who  was  killed  by  Israeli  troops  on  Wednesday.
